headline: Employers Enhanced Health Benefits in 2024, Adding Coverage for Weight-Loss Medications and IVF Despite Growing Health Costs, Mercer Survey Finds
summary: NEW YORK, November 20, 2024--Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, released results from its 2024 National Survey of Employer-Sponsored Health Plans.
